Description: The intersection is West Tambellup Road and Albany Hwy. There is poor vision in a southerly direction and restricted vision in a northerly direction. Sometimes if you think the road is clear you have to accelerate heavily in case a truck or fast moving vehicle is coming.

Muir Highway.  DANGEROUS. Narrow road for daily log trucks, caravan traffic and farm vehicles. The road is not wide enough as vehicle right side wheels are on the middle white line and the left side wheels are on broken/no road edging.  There are no overtaking lanes.
